{"title":"【033-041】个人信息表","slug":"hello-world4","date":"2022-09-28T11:14:59.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:28:33.968Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hello-world4.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                Document    &nbsp;&nbsp; 033 表单label标签<br>","covers":["https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/09/02/vIbNjK.jpg"],"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Document</title>\n</head>\n<body>\n    &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>033 表单label标签</h3><br>\n    <span id=\"more\"></span>\n     label双标签的使用可在表格中出现光标表格菜单,只读readonly和禁用disabled属性,<br><br>\n    <form action=\"\">\n        <label for=\"username\">请输入用户名:</label>\n        <input type=\"text\" id=\"username\"> <br><br>\n    您的手机号：<input type=\"text\" value=\"12345678\" readonly><br><br>\n    您的性别：<input type=\"radio\" name=\"gender\">男\n    <input type=\"radio\" name=\"gender\">女\n    <input type=\"radio\" name=\"gender\">保密\n    </form><br>\n    您的性别：<input type=\"radio\" name=\"gender\">男\n    <input type=\"radio\" name=\"gender\">女\n    <input type=\"radio\" name=\"gender\" disabled>保密\n    </form><br><br>\n    小技巧：input[type=\"radio\" name=gender]*3再label\n    &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>034 表单分组</h3><br>\n    带有边框和标题的表单控件字段集双标签fieldset，进行表单控件分组。嵌套双标签legend,说明的意思。<br><br>\n    <fieldset></fieldset><br><br>\n    边框作用就是相关字段进行视觉上的划分。<br><br>\n    <fieldset>\n        <legend>基础信息</legend><br><br>\n        用户名：<input type=\"text\"><br><br>   \n        密码：<input type=\"password\"><br><br>\n    </fieldset>\n    &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>035 表单按钮（上）</h3><br>\n    提交按钮：input里type属性为submit<br><br>\n    <form action=\"\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\">\n    </form><br><br>\n    form里定义action属性，填服务器地址<br><br>\n    <form action=\"https://windflower2022.github.io\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\">\n    </form><br><br>\n    form里定义target属性，_blank/_self<br><br>\n    <form action=\"https://windflower2022.github.io\" target=\"_blank\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\">\n    </form><br><br>\n    <form action=\"https://windflower2022.github.io\" target=\"_self\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\">\n    </form><br><br>\n    重置按钮：input里type属性为reset<br><br>\n    <form action=\"https://windflower2022.github.io\" target=\"_self\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\">\n        <input type=\"reset\">\n    </form><br><br>\n    普通按钮：input里type属性为button<br><br>\n    <form action=\"https://windflower2022.github.io\" target=\"_self\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\">\n        <input type=\"reset\">\n        <input type=\"button\">\n    </form><br><br>\n    <form action=\"https://windflower2022.github.io\" target=\"_self\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\">\n        <input type=\"reset\">\n        <input type=\"button\" value=\"普通按钮\">\n    </form><br><br>\n    反思：提交按钮也在input里添加属性value为注册，重置为登录。<br><br>\n    <form action=\"https://windflower2022.github.io\" target=\"_self\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\" value=\"注册\">\n        <input type=\"reset\" value=\"登录\">\n        <input type=\"button\" value=\"普通按钮\">\n    </form>\n    &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>036 表单按钮（下）</h3><br>\n    图像按钮：input里type属性为image,还要定义其属性src<br><br>\n    <form action=\"https://windflower2022.github.io\" target=\"_self\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\" value=\"注册\">\n        <input type=\"reset\" value=\"登录\">\n        <input type=\"button\" value=\"普通按钮\">\n        <input type=\"image\" src=\"图片地址\">\n    </form><br><br>\n    双标签button按钮：button<br><br>\n    <form action=\"https://windflower2022.github.io\" target=\"_self\">\n        姓名: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        邮箱: <input type=\"text\"><br><br>\n        <input type=\"submit\" value=\"注册\">\n        <input type=\"reset\" value=\"登录\">\n        <input type=\"button\" value=\"普通按钮\">\n        <input type=\"image\" src=\"图片地址\">\n        <button>button按钮</button>\n    </form><br><br>\n     &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>037-39 表单综合案例</h3><br>\n    <h1 align=\"center\">社区疫情流掉信息表</h1>\n    <p>&emsp;&emsp;请大家做好个人防护，如去过风险地区，请及时向社区报备。</p>\n    <form action=\"https://raink.net/api/html/signin\" target=\"_blank\">\n        <fieldset>\n            <legend>基本信息</legend>\n            <h4>1.您的名字</h4>\n            <input type=\"text\">\n            <h4>2.您的电话号码</h4>\n            <input type=\"text\" value=\"86113398214301\" onlyread>\n            <h4>3.您的性别</h4>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"gender\">男\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"gender\">女\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"gender\" disabled>保密\n            <h4>4.您的家庭住址</h4>\n            <select name=\"\" id=\"\">\n                <option value=\"\">哪个省</option>\n            </select>\n            <select name=\"\" id=\"\">\n                <option value=\"\">市</option>\n            </select>\n            <select name=\"\" id=\"\">\n                <option value=\"\">县</option>\n            </select>\n            <select name=\"\" id=\"\">\n                <option value=\"\">乡</option>\n            </select><br><br>\n            <textarea name=\"\" id=\"\" cols=\"65\" rows=\"4\">请输入详细地址</textarea>\n        </fieldset><br><br>\n            <legend>目前状况</legend>    \n            <h4>5.您现在的身体状况</h4>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">健康<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">发热<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">干咳<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">乏力<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">呼吸困难<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">咽痛<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">胸痛<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">肌肉酸痛<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">呕吐<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">腹泻<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">味觉异常<br><br>\n            <input type=\"checkbox\">嗅觉异常<br><br>\n         小技巧：input[type=\"checkbox\"]*12再tab\n            <h4>6.您的健康码颜色目前是</h4>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"color\">绿色\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"color\">黄色\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"color\">红色\n            <h4>7.是否在14天有个高中风险区旅居史</h4>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"close\">是\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"close\">否\n            <h4>8.疫苗接种情况</h4>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vaccines\">已接种第一针\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vaccines\">已接种第二针\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"vaccines\">已接种第三针    <br><br>   \n        <fieldset>\n            <legend>保密信息</legend>\n            <h4>1.身份证信息</h4>\n            正面：<input type=\"file\"><br><br>\n            反面：<input type=\"file\"><br><br>\n            <h4>2.学历信息（最高）</h4>\n            <select name=\"\" id=\"\">\n                <option value=\"\">研究生</option>\n                <option value=\"\">本科</option>\n                <option value=\"\">大专</option>\n                <option value=\"\">高中</option>\n                <option value=\"\">高中以下</option>\n            </select>\n            <h4>3.是否服兵役</h4>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"ismilitary\" id=\"yes\">\n            <label for=\"yes\">是</label>\n            <input type=\"radio\" name=\"ismilitary\" id=\"no\">\n            <label for=\"no\">否</label>\n            <h4>4.个人意见</h4>\n            <textarea name=\"\" id=\"\" cols=\"60\" rows=\"5\">请输入详细地址</textarea>\n        </fieldset><br><br>\n            <input type=\"submit\" value=\"上传信息\">\n            <input type=\"reset\" value=\"清空信息\">\n            <input type=\"image\" src=\"\" alt=\"提交\">\n        </form><br><br>\n        &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>040 表单数据采集和提交</h3><br>\n        <form action=\"https://raink.net/api/html/signin\">\n          手机号码：<input type=\"text\" name=\"pnumber\">  <br> <br>\n          密码框: <input type=\"password\" name=\"password\"><br> <br>\n          <input type=\"submit\" value=\"登录\"><br> <br>\n        </form><br> <br>\n        &nbsp;&nbsp; <h3>041 其它实用标签 </h3><br>\n        hr(horizontal)单标签，表水平线，作用是网页上画出一条水平分割线。视觉上将文档分成多个部分。<br> <br>\n        5个属性，width宽度,size高度,noshade去掉水平线阴影。color用于定义水平线颜色。align水平线水平对齐方式。<br> <br>\n        爱上一朵花的芬芳 爱一朵花的倔强\n        <hr width=\"300px\" size=\"10px\" align=\"left\" noshade color=\"green\">\n        爱上一朵花的姿态 它在黑夜中发亮<br> <br>\n        pre(preformatted)双标签：预格式化的文本，里面文本以固定宽度格式显示，保留了空格和换行。<br> <br>\n        <pre>\n            爱上一个人的目光\n            爱上一个人的家乡\n            爱上一个人的伤疤\n            他在记忆的远方\n        </pre>\n        map双标签:定义一个图像映射，就是一个图片的热点链接。点击图片实现链接跳转。属性name。<br> <br>嵌套area,定义图片的热点区域，其shape属性：\n        default所有区域；rect矩形；circle圆形；poly多边形。coords属性坐标，与shape配合使用。<br> <br>\n        <map name=\"\">\n            <area shape=\"circle\" coords=\"x,y,r\" href=\"目标地址\" alt=\"\">\n            <area shape=\"poly\" coords=\"x1,y1,x2,y2,x3,y3,...xn,yn\" href=\"目标地址\" alt=\"\">\n            <area shape=\"rect\" coords=\"x1,y1,x2,y2\" href=\"目标地址\" alt=\"\">   \n        </map>\n        <img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/09/02/vIbNjK.jpg\" alt=\"windflower\" usemap=\"#flower\"><br> <br>\n        <map name=\"flower\">\n            <area shape=\"rect\" coords=\"0,0,110,260\" href=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/09/15/vzF5es.jpg\" alt=\"ruyuan\">\n            <area shape=\"cirle\" coords=\"129,161,10\" href=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/09/10/vOAQsI.jpg\" alt=\"zhdjt\">\n        </map><br><br>       \n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"html","slug":"html","count":5,"path":"api/categories/html.json"}],"tags":[]}